metadata.name: 🐸 Last day @ Ethernia 🐸
metadata.description:
Its Special project for NFT20th anniversary for
Pepe, the legendary frog from comicbook  Boy’s club, by Matt Furie (2005) who’s favored by people all around the world. 20th anniversary will finally be reached in 2025, so we created special art by combining all 20 artworks. (Original1/1) Therefore, we demonstrate the 20th artwork and count back to the 1st  nft art  in 2025.  We will Keep every updating through LamboPhonic twitter🔷
